Method Detail

getNamingEntries

java.util.Map getNamingEntries(java.lang.String encName,
                               long timeout)
Lookup all the entries for the given name.

Typically a new instance is created for each redirect call and will cache the entries for each unique "encName".

Parameters:
encName - the URL-encoded remote agent name
timeout - timeout on lookup in milliseconds, zero for no timeout, or negative for non-blocking lookup.
Returns:
the naming service entries, or null if the naming service could not be accessed.
